<para style="q1">

<verse number="15" style="v" />I have always been afflicted and on the verge of death since my youth.</para>

<para style="q1">I have suffered from your terrors; I am in despair.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="16" style="v" />Your angry actions have passed over me,</para>

<para style="q1">and your terrifying deeds have annihilated me.</para>
